[DhtmlXQ_comment0]第四章 正马三兵对肋车边马[/DhtmlXQ_comment0]
[DhtmlXQ_comment11]过河车直攻弱马,这种走法首见于1976年江苏上海邀请赛,言穆江战胜胡荣华之战.[/DhtmlXQ_comment11]
[DhtmlXQ_comment13]正着.[/DhtmlXQ_comment13]
[DhtmlXQ_comment16]如改走士4进5,炮五平四,红方稳持先手.[/DhtmlXQ_comment16]
[DhtmlXQ_comment19]退车策应左翼,很有必要.[/DhtmlXQ_comment19]
[DhtmlXQ_comment20]弃卒通马,防止红炮右移.[/DhtmlXQ_comment20]
[DhtmlXQ_comment35]红方多兵较优.[/DhtmlXQ_comment35]
[DhtmlXQ_comment1_33]红必吃回一子占优.[/DhtmlXQ_comment1_33]
[DhtmlXQ_comment2_31]红有攻势占优.[/DhtmlXQ_comment2_31]
[DhtmlXQ_comment3_14]进车骑河引诱红车压马,控制局势发展,为攻三路打基础.[/DhtmlXQ_comment3_14]
[DhtmlXQ_comment3_15]平车压马正合黑方要求.如改走相三进一,红方先手.[/DhtmlXQ_comment3_15]
[DhtmlXQ_comment3_17]调整阵形策应左马.[/DhtmlXQ_comment3_17]
[DhtmlXQ_comment3_21]补士放任黑马出击失策.应改走炮八进三.[/DhtmlXQ_comment3_21]
[DhtmlXQ_comment3_34]如改走卒4平5,马八进七,双方对攻.[/DhtmlXQ_comment3_34]
[DhtmlXQ_comment3_36]各有顾忌.[/DhtmlXQ_comment3_36]
[DhtmlXQ_comment4_34]黑方多子较优.[/DhtmlXQ_comment4_34]
[DhtmlXQ_comment5_27]红方先手.[/DhtmlXQ_comment5_27]
[DhtmlXQ_comment6_29]炮五平三,马6进5,黑优.[/DhtmlXQ_comment6_29]
[DhtmlXQ_comment6_38]可成和棋.[/DhtmlXQ_comment6_38]
[DhtmlXQ_comment7_17]炮八平九,车2平3,车八进二,卒3进1,黑方先手.[/DhtmlXQ_comment7_17]
[DhtmlXQ_comment7_20]黑有对攻机会.[/DhtmlXQ_comment7_20]
